           <span class="uitext reviewText">Complex mystery lovers</span></div>

        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3642045-sue?shelf=around-the-world-in-52">around-the-world-in-52</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3642045-sue?shelf=mystery">mystery</a>, 
